ce_data : pd.Series\n    Field-wide statistics mapped to each source."]}, {"name": "hyperbolic.magnitudes.ref_flux_from_zp", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "m_0", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Convert the photometric zeropoint to the reference flux."]}, {"name": "hyperbolic.magnitudes.zp_from_ref_flux", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "flux", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Convert the reference flux to the photometric zeropoint"]}, {"name": "hyperbolic.magnitudes.estimate_zp", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "magnitude", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "flux", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Estimate the photometric zeropoint from a set of magnitudes and corresponding fluxes.\n\nParameters:\n-----------\nmagnitude : array-like\n    Magnitudes of objects.\nflux : array-like\n    Fluxes of objects.\n\nReturns:\n--------\nzp : array-like\n    Photometric zeropoint per object."]}, {"name": "hyperbolic.magnitudes.convert_flux", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "flux", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "zeropoint", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "target_zp", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Convert a flux measurement obtained with a given photometric zeropoint to a flux system with a\ndifferent photometric zeropoint.\n\nParameters:\n-----------\nflux : array-like\n    Input fluxes of objects.\nzeropoint : array-like\n    Photometric zeropoint (per source) corresponding to the input fluxes.\ntarget_zp : array-like\n    Photometric zeropoint (per source) for the output fluxes.\n\nReturns:\n--------\nflux : array-like\n    Output fluxes for the new photometric zeropoint."]}, {"name": "hyperbolic.magnitudes.estimate_b", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "zp", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "flux_error", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Estimate the smoothing factor for hyperbolic magnitudes in flux units for a given photometric\nzeropoint and flux errors.\n\nParameters:\n-----------\nzp : array-like\n    Photometric zeropoint (per source) for the output fluxes.\nflux_error : array-like\n    Flux error (per object).\n\nReturns:\n--------\nb : array-like\n    Estimate of the smoothing factor (per object)."]}, {"name": "hyperbolic.magnitudes.compute_classic_magnitude", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "flux", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "zeropoint", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "fill", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "float", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.float", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Compute the classical magnitude for a given flux measurement and photometric zeropoint.\n\nParameters:\n-----------\nflux : array-like\n    Input fluxes of objects.\nzeropoint : array-like\n    Photometric zeropoint (per object).\nfill : array-like\n    Fill value to use for objects with flux <= 0, defaults to NaN.\n\nReturns:\n--------\nmag : array-like\n    Classical magnitude for objects."]}, {"name": "hyperbolic.magnitudes.compute_classic_magnitude_error", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "flux", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "flux_error", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "fill", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "float", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.float", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Compute the error of the classical magnitude for a given flux measurement and error.\n\nParameters:\n-----------\nflux : array-like\n    Input fluxes of objects.\nflux_error : array-like\n    Input flux errors of objects.\nfill : array-like\n    Fill value to use for objects with flux <= 0, defaults to NaN.\n\nReturns:\n--------\nmag : array-like\n    Classical magnitude error for objects."]}, {"name": "hyperbolic.magnitudes.compute_magnitude", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "norm_flux", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "b", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Compute the hyperbolic magnitude for a given flux measurement and smoothing parameter b.\n\nParameters:\n-----------\nnorm_flux : array-like\n    Normalised fluxes (flux divided by reference flux) of objects.\nb : array-like\n    Smoothing parameter (per object).\n\nReturns:\n--------\nmag : array-like\n    Hyperbolic magnitude for objects."]}, {"name": "hyperbolic.magnitudes.compute_magnitude_error", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "norm_flux", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "b", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "norm_flux_err", "type": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Compute the error of the hyperbolic magnitude for a given flux measurement and error, and\nsmoothing parameter.\n\nParameters:\n-----------\nnorm_flux : array-like\n    Normalised fluxes (flux divided by reference flux) of objects.\nb : array-like\n    Smoothing parameter (per object).\nnorm_flux_err : array-like\n    Error of the normalised fluxes of objects.\n\nReturns:\n--------\nerror : array-like\n    Hyperbolic magnitude error for objects."]}, {"name": "hyperbolic.magnitudes.compute_flux_stats", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "flux", "type": {"name": "npt.NDArray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.NDArray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "error", "type": {"name": "npt.NDArray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.NDArray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "fields", "type": {"name": "npt.NDArray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.NDArray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "magnitudes", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "npt.NDArray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.NDArray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "zeropoint", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "npt.ArrayLike", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.ArrayLike", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "is_good", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "npt.NDArray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.typing.NDArray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "pd.DataFrame", "xref": {"fqname": "pandas.DataFrame", "project": "pandas"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Compute the median flux error, photometric zeropoint, and reference flux per field (e.g. spatial\nregions, telescope pointings, etc.). The field identifiers can be set to a single value to\ncompute the statistics globally. \n\nParameters:\n-----------\nflux : array-like\n    Input fluxes of objects.\nerror : array-like\n    Input flux er